T1  - On a lender of last resort with a central bank and a stability Fund
AU  - Callegari, Giovanni
AU  - Marimon, Ramon
AU  - Wicht, Adrien
AU  - Zavalloni, Luca
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 50
SP  - 106
EP  - 130
